snippet.title: Best VGM 2209 - Mega Man X3 - Gravity Beetle
snippet.description:
See also:
Best VGM 715 - https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GWaooxrlseo

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

SNES
Mega Man X3 (1996)
Gravity Beetle
Kinuyo Yamashita
